{"tid":1539070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日搭咗黨鐵，不過跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T01:00:02.000Z","uid":282118,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e479f54088c1ce66d7c113abd63b7d15f7f8e3f3","tid":1539070,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e470831f4d1ae0abbbed49c715d8297ad7fd03f","tid":1539070,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHJFfmd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHJFfmd.jpg&h=5166b6cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1baa8db757d7cd4998ea0cb5a709cf3e8ad74c1","tid":1539070,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f1b5163aec3b6d31ea60028e6c2505f98d185b","tid":1539070,"uid":192407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55a5aaac1e0bcc51e51eb6ecec04f224a54e480e","tid":1539070,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"今日都跳咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec2cfbb3017ffaa0b226b12b01ac33d3e7a4625","tid":1539070,"uid":117082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"由9月1開始chok閘"},{"pid":"5cea43bb4c6fe3a06d9e4a3b6d09b8d6e269e309","tid":1539070,"uid":211578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n8人離世<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e36b87fa06c6b627b9689943c8a3b8895d353045","tid":1539070,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"幾時都玩得　隨時都練得<br />\n唔洗一定要朝早<br />\n黑狗晨操先練<br />\n<br />\n<strong>黨鐵必須死！</strong>"},{"pid":"dbeaa839b9e70b47dcb1352dd2670256ce325a14","tid":1539070,"uid":221171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"我垃圾 比咗$1. 9黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#ass<br />\n不過weekend放假照跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6676ae11c9d66d736a21291131000cf157bb852","tid":1539070,"uid":212238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"想跳閘既入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1538653/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1538653/page/1</a><br />\n港鐵職員沒有告訴你的事"},{"pid":"4656a473d2f53d6f47d5aa3cfa404971df342c6e","tid":1539070,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing 5 demands, not 1 less?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb87110465e3399b4429ee2e20854ebfa52a8cf6","tid":1539070,"uid":2